creator: Storeino
descriptionHtml:
Storeino is the optimal solution you need to create your online store, follow the growth of your business and manage your entire activity,
Our platform allows you to create and manage your online business wherever you are without any additional costs and all on your mobile,
On Storeino application you can:
Manage your orders:
- Track your orders in real time with notifications of each order received on your store,
- Edit customer contact informations and products for each order,
- Contact your customers directly,
- Print delivery labels and invoices for your orders,
- Track and edit the status of your orders
Manage products:
- Add and edit products and variants,
- Define and manage the visibility of your products on your online store
Track and display statistics:
- Track and display the sales made on your online store per day, per week,
- Track orders by status in real time,
- Track and manage your shipments and deliveries,
General settings:
- Set up the languages of your online store,
- Add and edit your currencies and currency rates,
- Manage and edit the roles of your teams,
- Manage your store's payment methods,
descriptionShort: Storeino E-commerce Business Platform - Online Store Manager
